Action Under Water

If You are too long under the water,
you will die. But there's couple of places
where you can get up and breath.

When you are suddenly losing your health,
it doesn't mean that someone shot you.
Often it means that you don't have oxygen,
then you have to get to a place where you can
breath. It's easy to find the place, just look
around and somewhere in the ceiling
you maybe see a light, go there.
Or if you don't see those places,
keep looking, you will found them.
